title: Best of The Program | Guests: Alana Goodman & Daniel Halper | 7/10/20
description:
What is Joe Biden rambling on about this week? Alana Goodman and Daniel Halper, co-authors of “A Convenient Death: The Mysterious Demise of Jeffrey Epstein,” join to discuss the story so far: Could Epstein have been an intelligence asset, did he actually commit suicide, will Ghislaine Maxwell stay alive and testify, and will we ever know the full story?
